    "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/decision/morrison-cou1-accepted-2026",
    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2. The geometry revision of 2025-11-14 introduced a 0.03 mm tip clearance correction; the assessment team determined this change was not material to the inlet boundary condition data sourced from the PIV dataset (dataVintage 2025-10-21), as the revision affects only the local impeller tip recirculation and not bulk inlet flow profiles. On this basis, re-validation against updated geometry was not performed prior to submission. The relative hemolysis index RH = 0.83 satisfies the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. The package is accepted for regulatory submission supporting worst-case hemolysis operating condition identification for the Class II CPB device.",
